---
import Section from './layout/Section.astro';
import Container from './layout/Container.astro';
---

<Section aria-labelledby="why-copycodeai-title">
  <Container size="wide">
    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-soft sm:p-8 lg:p-10">
    <h2 id="why-copycodeai-title" class="text-3xl font-semibold text-ink-900">Why CopyCodeAI</h2>

    <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-sm text-slate-600">Practical engineering support for founders who need clarity before they scale.</p>

    <div class="mt-4 max-w-3xl space-y-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
      <p>Most early-stage teams move fast and leave structure for later.</p>
      <p>
        Those shortcuts turn into real problems: broken data flow, unclear consent logic, accessibility gaps,
        and AI features that are hard to scale.
      </p>
      <p>I help founders catch that early, without slowing the build down.</p>
    </div>

    <ul class="mt-6 grid gap-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <li class="flex gap-2 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-500" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>clearer data flow</span></li>
      <li class="flex gap-2 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-500" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>cleaner launch structure</span></li>
      <li class="flex gap-2 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-500" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>fewer avoidable compliance issues</span></li>
      <li class="flex gap-2 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-500" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>build decisions that hold up later</span></li>
    </ul>
    </article>
  </Container>
</Section>
